<inglise> Definitions </inglise>
<eesti> M&otilde;isted </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of this Regulation the following definitions shall apply: </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses kasutatakse j&auml;rgmisi m&otilde;isteid: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) "boarding ": the boarding of a fishing vessel within an organisation's area of competence by one or more authorised inspectors in order to make an inspection; </inglise>
<eesti> a) pardaleminek - &uuml;he v&otilde;i mitme volitatud inspektori minek m&otilde;ne organisatsiooni p&auml;devusalasse kuuluva kalalaeva pardale, et seal kontrollida; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) "transhipment ": unloading of any quantity of highly migratory fish and/or products from such fish from on board a fishing vessel to another vessel either at sea or in port, without the products having been recorded by a port State as landed; </inglise>
<eesti> b) &uuml;mberlaadimine - siirdekalade ja/v&otilde;i neist valmistatud toodete laadimine &uuml;he kalalaeva pardalt teisele kas merel v&otilde;i sadamas, olenemata nende kogusest ja ilma et sadamariik oleks tooted lossituna registreerinud; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) "landing ": unloading of any quantity of highly migratory fish and/or products from such fish from on board a fishing vessel to port or to land; </inglise>
<eesti> c) lossimine - siirdekalade ja/v&otilde;i neist valmistatud toodete mahalaadimine kalalaeva pardalt sadamas v&otilde;i maal, olenemata nende kogusest; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) "infringement ": any presumed act committed or omitted by a fishing vessel that is recorded in an inspection report and gives serious reason for suspecting a breach of the provisions of this Regulation or any other Regulation transposing a recommendation adopted by a regional organisation for one of the zones indicated in Article 2; </inglise>
<eesti> d) rikkumine - tegu, mille kalalaev on oletatavasti teinud v&otilde;i tegemata j&auml;tnud, mida on nimetatud kontrollaktis ja mis annab t&otilde;sist alust kahtlustada, et k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse v&otilde;i m&otilde;ne muu artiklis 2 nimetatud v&ouml;&ouml;ndi piirkondliku organisatsiooni vastuv&otilde;etud soovitust &uuml;lev&otilde;tva m&auml;&auml;ruse s&auml;tteid on rikutud; </eesti>
<inglise> (e) "vessel of a non-Contracting Party ": vessel observed and identified as engaged in fishing activities in one of the zones specified in Article 2 that is flying the flag of a country that is not a Contracting Party to the relevant regional organisation; </inglise>
